            </description>
        </image>
        <exercise>
            <title>Work with functions defined graphically</title>
            <statement>
                Given the graph of <m>y=g(x)</m> above, determine the following:
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            <m>y=g(3)</m> 
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            The solution(s) of <m>g(x)=2</m>.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
